"Huge ego. Sorry."

551
00:25:43,167 --> 00:25:44,834
Second, find a new career.

552
00:25:45,085 --> 00:25:46,285
You're never gonna sell anybody

553
00:25:46,295 --> 00:25:47,670
if you let them
control the agenda.

554
00:25:47,796 --> 00:25:49,196
And third,
I don't owe you anything.

555
00:25:49,298 --> 00:25:52,258
I'm not Wilson. I'm not gonna buy a
