556
00:26:01,894 --> 00:26:03,102
You okay?

557
00:26:03,229 --> 00:26:04,229
Yeah.

558
00:26:05,064 --> 00:26:06,773
Tell me how to do this.

559
00:26:06,982 --> 00:26:08,733
House says
people thank you after.

560
00:26:08,859 --> 00:26:10,068
It's not typical.

561
00:26:12,154 --> 00:26:14,405
