562
00:26:15,407 --> 00:26:17,909
All I can do now
is not make any more mistakes.

563
00:26:23,207 --> 00:26:26,209
First of all, stop thinking
you can minimize the hurt.

564
00:26:26,752 --> 00:26:28,753
A lot of people are afraid
of the word "dying."

565
00:26:28,879 --> 00:26:31,631
If you pussyfoot around it,
she's not going to read your mind.

566
00:26:31,757 --> 00:26:33,383
- Okay.
- No, it's not.

567
00:26:33,884 --> 00:26:34,968
When you look in her face,

568
