you're gonna feel
the instinct to temporize.

569
00:26:38,097 --> 00:26:39,013
Crush it.

570
00:26:39,473 --> 00:26:40,515
Yeah.

571
00:26:40,891 --> 00:26:42,225
Then wait.

572
00:26:42,768 --> 00:26:45,019
Give her time
